00:02:41.580 --> 00:02:43.740
My father was a Wesleyan Methodist.

00:02:43.820 --> 00:02:44.740
My mother was a Baptist.

00:02:45.920 --> 00:02:47.840
Lots of my friends were Quakers.

00:02:48.580 --> 00:02:52.540
I mean, America's built on Quakerism, a lot of it.

00:02:52.900 --> 00:02:54.360
It started off...

00:02:54.360 --> 00:02:58.940
The Mormons were in the same type, from the same ilk.

00:02:59.060 --> 00:03:00.380
A lot of Welsh people were Mormons.

